modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod increase starting items and add whole volume of one kind of book. Mainly for multiplayer, but not bad for single play.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod increase starting items and add whole volume of one kind of book. Mainly for multiplayer, but not bad for single play.

## Starting Items

* Pure Mineral [Water](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-drinks/) (2)
* Can of Chili (3)
* First Aid Bandage (5)
* Duke’s Casino Token (2000)
* Torch (1)
* Player Vending Machine (1) \*Instead of Land Claim Block
* Completed book bumdle (1)

[Download](https://www.mediafire.com/file/gjcf7fb8uwkh3ct/StartingItemPlus.zip)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/16568-a18-starting-item-plus-increase-some-items-and-add-whole-volume-of-one-kind-of-book/).

**Credits:** [Nanashi](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/nanashi/)
